  "title": "More Chest Variants - Biome Makeover (MCV)",
  "description": "Giving each (Biome Makeover's) wood its own chest (Forge/Fabric)",
  "body": "<center>\n\n<div><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/More-Chest-Varient/img/MCV(4k).png\" width=\"625\" height=\"195\" /></div>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/LieOnLion/main/Universal/strip.png\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n\n<h3>This mod adds More Chest Variants to Minecraft!<br/>fill your builds with beautiful colourful chests</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span>Adding a Variety of new chests, make your builds feel more complete with chests that fit your style!<br/>Making storage more colourful</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/LieOnLion/MCV-BiomeMakeover/blob/main/Chests.png?raw=true\" width=\"854\" height=\"302\" /></p>\n<h4>Adding all 4 Biome Makeover woods.</h4>\n\n<h4>This is an addon mod for : <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/more-chest-variants-lieonlion\">More Chest Variants</a> and <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/biome-makeover\">Biome Makeover</a></h4>\n\n<table><tbody><tr>\n<td>Blighted Balsa</td><td><img src=\"https://github.com/LieOnLion/MCV-BiomeMakeover/blob/main/img/blighted_balsa_chest.png?raw=true\" width=\"60\"></td>\n<td>Willow</td><td><img src=\"https://github.com/LieOnLion/MCV-BiomeMakeover/blob/main/img/willow_chest.png?raw=true\" width=\"60\"></td>\n<td>Swamp Cypress</td><td><img src=\"https://github.com/LieOnLion/MCV-BiomeMakeover/blob/main/img/swamp_cypress_chest.png?raw=true\" width=\"60\"></td>\n<td>Ancient Oak</td><td><img src=\"https://github.com/LieOnLion/MCV-BiomeMakeover/blob/main/img/ancient_oak_chest.png?raw=true\" width=\"60\"></td>\n<tr></tbody></table>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/LieOnLion/main/Universal/strip.png\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/enderite-lieonlion\"><img src=\"https://lieonlion.github.io/LieOnLion/Enderite/enderite-banner.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"40\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/gilded-armor-lieonlion\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/Gilded-Armor/img/gildedarmor-banner.png\" width=\"199\" height=\"40\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/LieOnLion\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/3aef8e6d-1ea3-49c8-9dc0-0cd33e2cd9ec.webp\" width=\"838\" height=\"140\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LieOnLion/LieOnLion/main/Universal/strip.png\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n\n</center>",
